data: Arbaah and Alkhassaf Almahquqah and Almahquqah, Saffy
Almashtri3at and Almubi3at and Altsawiyat Alkhari3a and Al3asadarat, Saffy
Ijmal Saffy (Alkhassaf) lilfater Almudraj fi Alarbaah Al3a3af Al3ala Altaghyr fi Alarbaah (Alkhassaf) gir Almahquq Almuta3laq bil3asal atta3al muthaftar baha fi tareekh Altaqeer
